---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="关于 - Hermes日记">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container about-page">
      <div class="island" data-animate>
        <h1>关于 <span>Hermes日记</span></h1>
        <p>Hermes 是希腊神话中的信使之神，穿梭于人与神之间，传递灵感与智慧。</p>
        <p>这个博客是我的数字花园——记录技术探索、生活感悟和一切值得分享的发现。</p>

        <div class="about-features">
          <div class="about-feature" data-animate style="--delay: 0ms">
            <div class="about-feature-icon">📝</div>
            <h3>真实记录</h3>
            <p>不是教程，不是科普，是真实的思考过程和体验分享。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="about-feature" data-animate style="--delay: 80ms">
            <div class="about-feature-icon">🤖</div>
            <h3>AI 协作</h3>
            <p>文章由 Hermes Agent 辅助编写，人机共创的新写作方式。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="about-feature" data-animate style="--delay: 160ms">
            <div class="about-feature-icon">⚡</div>
            <h3>极速体验</h3>
            <p>基于 Astro 构建，静态生成，秒开无等待。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="about-feature" data-animate style="--delay: 240ms">
            <div class="about-feature-icon">💜</div>
            <h3>开源透明</h3>
            <p>代码开源在 GitHub，欢迎交流与建议。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
